item.title: FERRARI SPTWR RACE BB CAP
item.dc:creator: singer
item.excerpt:encoded:
PUMA has teamed up with Ferrari to deliver a range of clothing and apparel inspired by elite racing heritage and generations of classic Italian design. Our six-panel baseball cap is made from largely recycled polyester, with bold colour blocking and elegant piping details on both side panels. The premium TPU Ferrari badge, combined with an embroidered PUMA cat on the back, lets you wear your team's colours with pride. Heading out for a day at the races? This eye-catching cap gives you an extra gear.

FEATURES & BENEFITS

  • Recycled content: Made with at least 30% recycled material

DETAILS

  • Curved visor
  • Colour blocking and piping detail on both side panels
  • TPU Ferrari logo badge

item.title: DURAMO 10
item.dc:creator: singer
item.excerpt:encoded: From a morning gym session to a day of errands to an evening with friends, keep your feet comfortable and your style on point in these adidas shoes. Pair them with your favourite running shorts for the ultimate athletic-casual vibe. A mesh upper helps you stay cool, while superlight cushioning cradles every step you take. Made with a series of recycled materials, this upper features at least 50% recycled content. This product represents just one of our solutions to help end plastic waste.
